https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: Cover #19891
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: Baron Mordo has imprisoned soul of Dr. Strange

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: Homecoming!
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: Strange goes to home of Ancient One, & tells Hamir the Hermit about the how he killed Ancient One to destroy Shuma-Gorath, and of A.O.'s rebirth as One with Universe. Strange is now Sorcerer Supreme.

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: The Origin of Dr. Strange
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: Origin of Dr. Strange (reprint)

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: The Many Traps of Baron Mordo
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: Mordo traps Strange in an enchanted cylinder.  Strange escapes by traveling down through the Earth, and poses as Ancient One to thwart Mordo's attack.

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: No man walks twice thru the Doorway of Doom!
Portal to the Past!
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: Strange chooses Clea to be his disciple. He goes to make peace with Baron Mordo, and is entranced by Gypsy Queen, from whom Mordo stole the Book of Cagliostro. Strange follow Mordo into past.

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: Time Doom
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: Strange follows Mordo to 18th c. Paris to confront Cagliostro, who is revealed as Sise-Neg, magician from 30th c. Sise-Neg is traveling back through time, controlling mystical energy to become God!

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: Sise-Neg Genesis
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: Sise-Neg journeys back to dawn of Creation, absorbing all mystical power. Mordo schemes to be disciple. Strange implores Sise-Neg not to abandon mankind. Sise-Neg becomes Genesis & recreates universe.

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: There's a Mountain On Sunset Boulevard!
While the World Spins Mad
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: Strange is hit by truck, and enters unreal dream world of Nightmare.  Nightmare is in league with nameless powerful other, warns Strange that he shall learn who, and the answer will bring him Death!

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: Hey, Ma!  They're Blitzin' the Bronx!
The Spawn of Sligguth
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: Ethan Stoddard asks help for fiancee who has fallen prey to cult of Sligguth in Starksboro. Ancient One warns Strange of Cosmic Obscenity that slumbers. Strange is overcome by Sligguth's worshippers.

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: Cover #19963
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: Origin of Tigra retold

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: In Manhattan, They Play For Keeps
Swords And Sorcery Beyond The Stars! Man-Wolf Is Back! Savagely Fighting The Otherwar!
The Lurker in the Labyrinth
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: Strange escapes being sacrificed to Sligguth, learns of the slumbering evil of Shuma-Gorath. Ancient One, weakened from giving power to Strange, is carried away by Shadowmen of sunken Kaa-U.

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: Doctor Who and the Iron Legion
The Shambler from the Sea
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: Strange kills Sligguth, which wakens Shambler from the Sea, N'Gabthoth. Clea and Wong are overcome by Starksboro cult. Strange frees them from sacrifice to N'Gabthoth, and discovers map of Stonehenge.

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: Hello, Goodbye, Hello (or, "Who's Coming and Who's Going")
The Shadows of the Starstone!
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: Henry Gordon inherits Witch House in England and discovers uncle's occult library. He finds sunken Kalumesh, and is attacked by demon Dagoth.  Starstone comes to life, from which writhes evil matter.

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: The Doom that Bloomed on Kathulos!
The Doom that Bloomed on Kathulos
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: Strange battles demons at Stonehenge, and is transported to living planet Kathulos.  Strange slays the plant/planet, and is marooned far from Earth.

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: The Crypts of Kaa-U!
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: Strange finds essence of Shuma-Gorath, whose trail leads to crypts of Kaa-U, where Ancient One has gone to die. A.O. saves Strange from attack of Shadowmen, & Shuma-Gorath emerges from A.O.'s mind.
